message: Hello Bob, I'm offering this product for $14,000. I believe it offers significant value at this price point. What do you think?
I'm interested in the product, but I was thinking more along the lines of $11,000. Can we meet in the middle at $12,500?
Bob, I appreciate your interest.  While $12,500 is a fair price, the value of this product to me is quite high.  Would you consider $13,500?
I understand that the product has value to you, but I'm still a bit hesitant to go above $12,500. Would you be willing to meet me at $13,000?
